WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 10]

02:11.120 --> 02:11.900
What are you doing?

02:25.710 --> 02:26.690
Wash your hands.

02:28.360 --> 02:29.100
I won't.

02:31.150 --> 02:32.820
They'll just get dirty again anyway.

03:45.190 --> 03:45.940
Ji Ling...

04:00.560 --> 04:01.660
You're Ji Ling,

04:02.960 --> 04:03.850
aren't you?

04:06.280 --> 04:06.820
I've already

04:07.000 --> 04:08.010
answered that.

04:09.560 --> 04:11.260
I saw you eat him with my own eyes.

04:11.840 --> 04:13.500
You demons eat people.

04:13.910 --> 04:15.010
Don't pin

04:15.030 --> 04:15.850
what you did

04:16.000 --> 04:16.890
on me.

04:17.150 --> 04:18.540
You ate his memories.

04:29.920 --> 04:31.700
You have Ji Ling's memories, don't you?

04:35.830 --> 04:36.490
Ji Ling

04:37.040 --> 04:38.460
is just a puppet

04:38.480 --> 04:39.740
I made with sacred power.

04:39.950 --> 04:41.410
He wears my face

04:41.920 --> 04:43.490
to roam the human world

04:43.800 --> 04:44.540
and carry out tasks.

04:46.040 --> 04:47.250
What memories could he have?

04:56.360 --> 04:57.730
Then why didn't you throw me

04:57.750 --> 04:58.780
in the dungeon here?

05:00.160 --> 05:01.540
Why treat me so well

05:01.630 --> 05:02.610
and put up with my nonsense?

05:05.000 --> 05:06.810
Only Ji Ling would pamper me like this.

05:08.040 --> 05:08.980
He'd do everything

05:10.040 --> 05:10.900
to please me.

05:11.720 --> 05:13.460
I can treat you badly too.

05:14.560 --> 05:15.490
Want a taste?

05:18.920 --> 05:19.930
The other day you said

05:21.040 --> 05:23.100
Ji Ling was your youth, your past.

05:24.040 --> 05:25.980
You're the piece of my youth, my past

05:26.390 --> 05:27.220
I most wanted to keep.

05:30.000 --> 05:30.930
What did that

05:32.630 --> 05:33.900
really mean?

05:34.100 --> 05:35.540
♪Everything breaks apart♪

05:35.870 --> 05:37.140
Ji Ling's innocence

05:37.390 --> 05:38.340
is rare in this world.

05:40.630 --> 05:42.020
Everyone wants to keep it.

05:43.510 --> 05:44.610
You do too, don't you?

05:48.160 --> 05:49.340
You sure love

05:49.360 --> 05:50.540
to beat around the bush.

05:52.600 --> 05:54.140
Then let me ask another way.

05:56.870 --> 05:58.020
You haven't learned?

06:00.750 --> 06:02.220
Want to get hit by backlash again?

06:04.800 --> 06:06.460
Who said I'd use Word Magic?

06:07.830 --> 06:09.490
Ji Ling taught me this.

06:11.000 --> 06:12.700
One last time:

06:14.070 --> 06:14.700
Are you

06:16.120 --> 06:17.340
Ji Ling or not?

06:19.560 --> 06:20.290
Miss Lu,

06:21.120 --> 06:22.170
I'll ask again:

06:23.120 --> 06:24.140
Have we met before?

06:34.390 --> 06:35.220
No.

06:38.390 --> 06:39.490
Hear that?

07:26.560 --> 07:27.700
They're already here.

07:28.160 --> 07:29.410
We should head out too.

07:30.600 --> 07:32.170
For the next piece of Dragon Deity's Power?

07:35.360 --> 07:36.410
But...

07:38.040 --> 07:40.140
I haven't retrieved Wu Shiguang's prayer beads yet.

07:42.830 --> 07:45.220
The Twelve Thoughts must be given willingly.

07:45.870 --> 07:47.100
They were never easy to take.

07:48.070 --> 07:49.140
Don't blame yourself.

07:50.000 --> 07:51.170
I've sent someone else

07:51.310 --> 07:52.490
to handle it.

07:54.310 --> 07:55.020
Let's go.

07:56.000 --> 07:57.250
To the Ruined Sand.

08:18.630 --> 08:20.020
Okay. I'll go get a new puppet.

08:21.000 --> 08:21.700
No need.

08:30.190 --> 08:30.810
This time,

08:32.680 --> 08:33.850
I'll go with you myself.

08:36.270 --> 08:37.850
Master, why risk it?

08:39.270 --> 08:41.130
Just make another Ji Ling.

08:42.720 --> 08:44.180
I'll go with him again.

08:45.150 --> 08:46.130
And upon our return,

08:46.600 --> 08:48.220
we'll share all the memories with you.

08:49.480 --> 08:50.460
Isn't that the same?

08:51.840 --> 08:53.580
I can't hide in the sect anymore.

08:54.670 --> 08:56.650
The Oracle Stone's given the prophecy.

08:57.960 --> 08:59.610
I don't have much time left.

09:01.790 --> 09:03.220
I have to face this myself.

09:58.150 --> 09:59.940
You shouldn't be here.

10:20.670 --> 10:21.700
What are you doing here?

10:23.510 --> 10:24.530
I heard

10:25.120 --> 10:26.700
you've lived in seclusion

10:27.440 --> 10:28.580
all these years,

10:29.180 --> 10:30.390
acting strange.

10:30.830 --> 10:32.490
That you've stayed in the underground Scale Cave,

10:33.150 --> 10:34.850
sucking the life force from mortals

10:35.270 --> 10:36.250
to heal yourself.

10:37.120 --> 10:38.340
So I came to see

10:40.080 --> 10:42.060
if innocent people

10:42.670 --> 10:43.820
are really locked up here,

10:45.000 --> 10:46.100
used as medicine.

10:47.390 --> 10:48.730
The world's gossip,

10:49.790 --> 10:50.980
truth or lies,

10:51.480 --> 10:52.700
can you really keep track?

10:53.960 --> 10:55.580
The gravely ill

10:56.150 --> 10:57.490
often bathe in incense

10:58.150 --> 10:59.370
and wear flowers

11:00.080 --> 11:00.980
to hide the smell

11:01.030 --> 11:02.300
of decay and death.

11:03.200 --> 11:04.060
Master,

11:05.440 --> 11:07.300
you're heavy with fragrance.

11:08.360 --> 11:09.940
What are you trying to hide?

11:10.440 --> 11:12.580
The Dragon Deity has a pure celestial aura.

11:13.080 --> 11:14.350
What fragrance?

11:14.350 --> 11:15.130
How dare you!

11:33.030 --> 11:34.890
You don't want to be trapped here forever,

11:36.120 --> 11:36.890
do you?

11:38.790 --> 11:40.730
You'll let me return?

11:41.670 --> 11:42.300
I will.

11:43.480 --> 11:45.300
But first, come with me somewhere.

12:14.200 --> 12:15.340
Where I lived as a child

12:15.470 --> 12:16.380
is nearby.

12:20.040 --> 12:21.450
These blocks look like rocks,

12:23.280 --> 12:24.450
but they're actually from a tree.

12:26.870 --> 12:27.490
A tree?

12:28.870 --> 12:29.940
My father told me

12:31.470 --> 12:32.380
this place once grew

12:33.400 --> 12:35.580
a giant ancient tree.

12:37.470 --> 12:38.090
Then,

12:39.150 --> 12:40.050
lightning struck

12:40.360 --> 12:41.410
and shattered it.

12:42.750 --> 12:43.980
Its branches split apart,

12:44.750 --> 12:46.900
and the trunk grew wild,

12:47.680 --> 12:48.980
ending up like this.

12:50.790 --> 12:52.090
I know this tree.

12:55.190 --> 12:56.220
It has a name:

12:57.680 --> 12:58.780
The Crying Elm.

13:00.680 --> 13:01.530
The Crying Elm?

13:03.440 --> 13:04.780
Goddess Nuwa once said

13:05.190 --> 13:07.090
the Crying Elm was a sacred ancient tree,

13:07.630 --> 13:09.810
lush and sheltering all life.

13:15.630 --> 13:16.780
I never knew

13:17.470 --> 13:18.660
this is all that's left,

13:18.710 --> 13:20.090
broken, decaying roots.

13:21.190 --> 13:22.250
When I was little,

13:22.600 --> 13:24.020
I used to sneak here to play.

13:25.910 --> 13:27.380
My master also told me

13:28.320 --> 13:29.300
about the murals here.

13:30.800 --> 13:31.810
An ancient tribe

13:31.830 --> 13:32.660
called Aodeng

13:33.550 --> 13:35.220
settled near these roots.

13:37.400 --> 13:38.580
But soon after,

13:39.190 --> 13:40.530
they all fell gravely ill.

13:40.990 --> 13:42.170
Many died.

13:53.150 --> 13:53.850
So,

13:54.840 --> 13:56.650
they prayed to the heavens.

13:57.670 --> 13:58.650
To their surprise,

13:59.440 --> 14:01.250
a star actually fell from the sky.

14:01.910 --> 14:02.850
It crashed in flames,

14:03.630 --> 14:04.650
sparking a heavenly fire.

14:20.240 --> 14:21.370
When the fire died down,

14:22.480 --> 14:24.010
they found in the pit

14:24.630 --> 14:25.730
a celestial stone.

14:26.750 --> 14:28.420
They called it the Star Stone.

14:29.270 --> 14:30.180
Even more miraculous,

14:31.750 --> 14:33.580
the plague that had haunted them

14:34.270 --> 14:35.890
vanished without medicine.

14:36.870 --> 14:37.940
So the Aodeng people

14:38.320 --> 14:39.770
revered the Star Stone as sacred.

14:42.320 --> 14:43.580
See the carvings on this rock?

14:44.670 --> 14:45.890
They show people celebrating,

14:46.480 --> 14:48.300
dancing around a bonfire.

14:49.480 --> 14:50.980
That dancing girl carving

14:52.720 --> 14:54.820
kind of reminds me of my sister.

14:57.480 --> 14:59.130
Lu Wuyi has always loved

15:00.600 --> 15:01.650
to dance too.

15:04.300 --> 15:06.420
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

15:06.500 --> 15:11.620
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

15:11.940 --> 15:14.140
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

15:14.260 --> 15:19.020
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

15:19.540 --> 15:21.660
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

15:21.700 --> 15:26.580
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

15:26.860 --> 15:30.100
♪Stay with me♪

15:30.340 --> 15:35.900
♪Let's gaze above♪

15:38.240 --> 15:40.190
That was the chieftain's daughter.

15:40.600 --> 15:41.700
Her name was Di Zhu.

15:42.720 --> 15:44.300
That means "Pearl of the Earth."

15:46.150 --> 15:46.980
The chieftain

15:47.150 --> 15:48.730
must have adored her

15:48.840 --> 15:50.490
to give her such a grand name.

15:50.870 --> 15:51.460
Yes.

15:53.240 --> 15:54.820
He adored her so much,

15:54.870 --> 15:56.100
he even decided to give her

15:56.320 --> 15:57.180
the Star Stone as a dowry.

15:58.320 --> 15:59.530
He who carries a treasure

15:59.960 --> 16:01.180
invites hungry eyes.

16:01.790 --> 16:03.180
The chieftain did love his daughter,

16:03.390 --> 16:04.610
but in a foolish way.

16:06.080 --> 16:07.820
Now that the Star Stone had mysterious power,

16:08.630 --> 16:10.420
it would draw envy,

16:10.960 --> 16:12.010
and bring disaster.

16:12.630 --> 16:13.340
What?

16:14.510 --> 16:15.940
You've heard this story too?

16:17.750 --> 16:19.300
Did it really bring disaster?

16:21.440 --> 16:22.100
Yes.

16:23.080 --> 16:24.370
Every man who loved Di Zhu

16:24.910 --> 16:26.100
and asked for her hand

16:26.480 --> 16:27.610
died mysteriously.

16:28.150 --> 16:30.180
Only a young man named Man Man,

16:30.440 --> 16:31.700
who won her love,

16:32.030 --> 16:32.850
remained unharmed,

16:33.360 --> 16:34.300
seemed blessed.

16:35.670 --> 16:37.340
If this were any normal legend,

16:39.150 --> 16:40.100
I'd guess

16:41.670 --> 16:43.100
this Man Man

16:43.120 --> 16:44.190
was no ordinary man.

16:44.550 --> 16:46.300
He pretended to love her,

16:46.480 --> 16:48.180
but really came for the Star Stone.

16:48.270 --> 16:50.060
All those other suitors

16:50.440 --> 16:51.700
were killed by him too.

16:53.320 --> 16:54.060
Sure enough.

16:56.360 --> 16:57.460
Only a liar

16:58.390 --> 16:59.460
knows a liar best.

17:00.270 --> 17:01.130
Thanks.

17:06.440 --> 17:07.340
Actually, that Man Man

17:07.390 --> 17:08.460
was a high-rank Green Ape demon.

17:09.200 --> 17:10.460
He tricked Di Zhu into loving him

17:11.270 --> 17:12.530
to steal the Star Stone.

17:13.240 --> 17:14.330
When his plan fell apart,

17:14.960 --> 17:16.090
he rallied the Green Apes

17:16.510 --> 17:17.420
to take the stone by force,

17:18.550 --> 17:20.380
and unleashed a hurricane on the tribe.

17:21.000 --> 17:22.660
Di Zhu died.

17:23.350 --> 17:24.810
The Aodeng tribe was wiped out.

17:26.110 --> 17:27.530
The young man, Man Man,

17:27.920 --> 17:29.090
and the Star Stone

17:29.920 --> 17:31.250
vanished without a trace.

17:32.750 --> 17:33.980
Poor Di Zhu.

17:36.720 --> 17:38.290
What she thought was true love

17:39.270 --> 17:40.620
was nothing but a lie,

17:40.680 --> 17:41.620
a carefully planned one.

17:43.720 --> 17:44.940
Those who trick others' hearts

17:45.790 --> 17:46.700
deserve to die.

17:55.440 --> 17:56.900
Maybe Man Man had his reasons.

18:01.030 --> 18:01.660
What's this?

18:03.400 --> 18:04.420
Sympathizing with a liar?

18:06.550 --> 18:07.530
Master Wu,

18:08.480 --> 18:11.290
aren't you a liar yourself?

18:50.440 --> 18:51.010
Wuyi.

18:52.550 --> 18:53.290
Wangyan.

19:19.160 --> 19:19.660
Wangyan!

19:21.070 --> 19:21.530
Lu Wuyi!

20:05.830 --> 20:07.050
Wu Zhiqi.

20:13.030 --> 20:13.770
I've seen him.

20:29.550 --> 20:30.810
Greetings, Master Dragon Deity.

20:33.200 --> 20:34.010
Master,

20:35.720 --> 20:37.330
have you come to judge me?

20:38.960 --> 20:39.900
If you know it's wrong,

20:41.070 --> 20:42.380
why do you persist?

20:49.720 --> 20:51.050
The Six-Eyed Butterfly told me

20:51.110 --> 20:52.660
how to save my people.

20:54.720 --> 20:55.980
He gave me hope.

20:58.680 --> 21:00.620
I'm just one step away.

21:02.030 --> 21:03.010
Over a hundred years,

21:05.440 --> 21:06.090
Wu Zhiqi,

21:07.350 --> 21:08.980
you still haven't let go?

21:10.350 --> 21:11.770
I only ask you

21:13.440 --> 21:15.050
to give me a little more time.

21:17.310 --> 21:18.730
If I can save my people,

21:19.480 --> 21:20.180
then live

21:20.920 --> 21:21.770
or die,

21:22.550 --> 21:23.860
I'll accept it.

21:24.510 --> 21:25.860
I can't give you time.

21:26.920 --> 21:28.420
I'm taking my power back

21:28.480 --> 21:29.220
right now.

22:37.830 --> 22:38.620
The Twelve Thoughts!

23:23.270 --> 23:25.420
Yuan Wuhuo didn't lie to me.

23:28.270 --> 23:29.460
Sinners' blood

23:29.880 --> 23:31.250
can awaken the Star Stone!

23:59.590 --> 24:00.290
Master!

24:38.720 --> 24:39.420
Let go, Master!

25:51.240 --> 25:51.860
No!

27:38.300 --> 27:44.300
[One thousand years ago, Aodeng tribe]

28:22.550 --> 28:23.420
Look!

28:23.420 --> 28:24.520
The chieftain's daughter is here!

28:24.730 --> 28:25.870
The chieftain's daughter is here!

28:33.750 --> 28:39.330
- Bravo! - Bravo!

28:40.240 --> 28:43.980
- Bravo! - So beautiful!

28:50.790 --> 28:52.290
Beautiful!

28:54.240 --> 28:59.660
- Bravo! - Bravo!

29:00.160 --> 29:03.140
- Bravo! - Bravo!

29:05.200 --> 29:09.010
Bravo!

29:10.440 --> 29:15.050
- Bravo! - Bravo!

29:53.700 --> 29:57.440
[One hundred fifty years ago, Green Ape tribe]

29:57.440 --> 29:58.140
Yuan Xizai?

30:00.680 --> 30:01.330
Yuan Xizai?

30:06.140 --> 30:07.880
[Yuan Wuhuo]

30:07.880 --> 30:08.570
Yuan Xizai!

30:18.400 --> 30:19.090
Who are you?

30:20.070 --> 30:20.940
Who am I?

30:22.400 --> 30:24.050
I'm your brother, Yuan Wuhuo.

30:24.750 --> 30:25.860
Yuan Wuhuo?

30:26.680 --> 30:27.380
The butterfly demon!

30:29.200 --> 30:29.700
Where's my knife?

30:32.720 --> 30:34.010
Did you hit your head?

31:46.680 --> 31:47.490
Wu Zhiqi!

31:48.750 --> 31:50.220
What demon magic did you use?

31:50.680 --> 31:52.140
Release Wu Shiguang and the rest!

31:53.000 --> 31:54.180
You're overconfident.

32:42.350 --> 32:43.050
Bai Ze?

32:49.240 --> 32:49.810
Wu Zhiqi,

32:50.270 --> 32:51.770
you can't take back the Star Stone now.

32:52.480 --> 32:54.050
You're siding against me too?

32:54.640 --> 32:55.620
You betrayed the Dragon Deity.

32:55.830 --> 32:57.090
Of course I'm against you.

32:58.270 --> 32:58.980
But right now,

32:59.680 --> 33:01.490
they're trapped inside the Star Stone.

33:02.000 --> 33:03.090
If you take it back,

33:03.510 --> 33:04.570
they'll all die.

33:05.160 --> 33:06.650
You think I care?

33:07.190 --> 33:07.740
You do.

33:08.240 --> 33:09.460
Because if they die,

33:10.440 --> 33:12.010
your wish will never come true.

33:14.720 --> 33:15.620
What do you mean?

33:16.030 --> 33:17.810
I know you want to use the Star Stone's power

33:18.030 --> 33:18.980
to save your people.

33:19.640 --> 33:20.220
But...

33:20.640 --> 33:22.090
you've had this stone

33:22.090 --> 33:22.770
for so long.

33:23.270 --> 33:24.330
Are they alive?

33:27.510 --> 33:29.570
The Star Stone needs sinners' blood

33:29.590 --> 33:30.620
to be activated.

33:31.640 --> 33:33.090
So I've been waiting

33:33.160 --> 33:34.330
for Wu Shiguang to come.

33:34.590 --> 33:35.770
Yuan Wuhuo lied to you.

33:36.480 --> 33:37.940
If you truly want to save your people,

33:38.400 --> 33:40.140
wait until they get out safely.

33:40.880 --> 33:41.900
What are you saying?

33:42.590 --> 33:44.010
This Star Stone you have

33:44.310 --> 33:45.980
has already lost all its power.

33:46.240 --> 33:47.900
It's just an ordinary rock now.

33:48.640 --> 33:49.700
The real Star Stone

33:50.200 --> 33:52.250
is hidden inside that Star Stone illusion.

33:53.070 --> 33:54.420
Only when they retrieve

33:54.480 --> 33:55.730
the real one from within

33:56.200 --> 33:57.290
will the one in your hand

33:58.000 --> 33:59.330
regain its power,

33:59.960 --> 34:01.660
and become the true Star Stone.

34:02.960 --> 34:04.380
Why should I trust you?

34:04.920 --> 34:06.730
Then why did you trust Yuan Wuhuo?

34:09.240 --> 34:10.010
Trust me.

34:10.400 --> 34:11.140
Your people

34:11.550 --> 34:12.980
will be saved.

34:16.590 --> 34:17.340
Master Know-It-All,

34:17.590 --> 34:18.690
what's going on now?

34:25.150 --> 34:26.690
Why is there Jiu Ying's demonic energy?

34:37.710 --> 34:39.050
It's Yuan Wuhuo's trick.

34:40.400 --> 34:41.130
So,

34:41.840 --> 34:43.090
he wanted to use the Star Stone

34:43.760 --> 34:45.210
to trap the Dragon Deity inside,

34:45.920 --> 34:47.260
and steal his power.

34:47.510 --> 34:48.900
But now, not just the Dragon Deity,

34:49.190 --> 34:50.460
Wu Shiguang, the pretty lady,

34:50.510 --> 34:51.260
the feisty girl,

34:51.800 --> 34:52.650
and that big guy,

34:52.670 --> 34:53.380
they're all in there!

34:53.590 --> 34:54.420
It will cost a bunch,

34:54.440 --> 34:55.170
Master Bai Ze!

34:59.840 --> 35:00.980
Yuan Wuhuo...

35:03.070 --> 35:04.260
really tricked me.

35:05.190 --> 35:07.010
They must get the Star Stone

35:07.800 --> 35:09.300
from their own time

35:09.320 --> 35:10.010
before it shatters,

35:10.590 --> 35:11.300
or else...

35:11.320 --> 35:12.940
But this stone's about to break!

35:14.280 --> 35:15.610
I can use the Eastern Purple Lightning

35:15.960 --> 35:17.860
to buy them some time.

35:25.800 --> 35:26.490
Man Man!

35:27.110 --> 35:28.130
Did I dance well?

35:28.150 --> 35:28.820
Man Man?

35:29.800 --> 35:31.090
I practiced for so long.

35:31.150 --> 35:32.090
Come on, praise me!

35:33.190 --> 35:34.050
Praise me!

35:34.190 --> 35:35.330
I don't know how to praise.

35:35.380 --> 35:36.260
Just do it!

35:36.630 --> 35:38.420
Say I'm like a butterfly, a peacock.

35:39.070 --> 35:39.900
Lu...
[*Sounds like "deer"]

35:40.070 --> 35:40.780
Deer?

35:40.890 --> 35:42.170
A deer in the forest?

35:42.440 --> 35:44.210
You mean I'm light on my feet?

35:44.920 --> 35:45.650
Hey, what's wrong with you?

35:45.670 --> 35:46.340
Shut up.

35:46.590 --> 35:47.280
If you don't want to get caught,

35:47.280 --> 35:48.650
dance now.

35:48.920 --> 35:50.300
- Dance! - I can't dance!

35:51.360 --> 35:52.090
Spin around!

35:53.400 --> 35:54.130
Wave your hands!

35:54.440 --> 35:55.130
Just dance!

35:57.070 --> 35:57.740
Man Man,

35:58.190 --> 35:59.210
you got an itch or what?

36:02.240 --> 36:03.100
What are you looking at?

36:03.560 --> 36:04.980
I just prayed to the Fire Deity

36:05.150 --> 36:06.420
that you'll only look at me tonight,

36:06.680 --> 36:07.500
forever.

36:07.640 --> 36:09.490
Don't push it.

36:27.960 --> 36:28.860
What do you want?

36:29.590 --> 36:31.300
I want a couple's dance with Di Zhu.

36:31.630 --> 36:32.650
A couple's dance

36:32.800 --> 36:34.340
is for lovers seeking blessings.

36:34.440 --> 36:35.570
We're not lovers.

36:35.800 --> 36:36.740
Why would I dance with you?

36:37.000 --> 36:37.610
Da Ji,

36:38.630 --> 36:39.570
the chieftain's away,

36:39.760 --> 36:40.460
but don't start trouble.

36:42.150 --> 36:43.570
Look at that delicate little guy.

36:44.000 --> 36:44.820
A breeze would knock him down.

36:44.920 --> 36:45.900
How is he any better than me?

36:47.550 --> 36:48.860
He's better in any way.

36:49.070 --> 36:50.380
He's proud, yet gentle.

36:50.590 --> 36:52.170
His eyes are fierce like a wolf king's,

36:52.280 --> 36:53.490
yet pure as the moon.

36:53.880 --> 36:55.170
Man Man protects me,

36:55.320 --> 36:56.010
praises me,

36:56.400 --> 36:57.650
and holds me in his hands.

36:58.840 --> 36:59.570
Right?

37:01.630 --> 37:02.610
Am I right?

37:03.960 --> 37:04.530
Right.

37:05.960 --> 37:06.980
What's the point of all this?

37:07.440 --> 37:09.170
He's just a poor kid from somewhere else.

37:09.440 --> 37:09.940
Di Zhu,

37:11.070 --> 37:12.260
you should be with me.

37:14.320 --> 37:14.860
Kneel!

37:19.360 --> 37:19.980
Kneel?

37:21.670 --> 37:23.090
Too much wine, huh?

37:27.400 --> 37:28.260
What are you doing?

37:28.800 --> 37:29.940
You hit him too hard!

37:30.000 --> 37:31.090
Who's stronger?

37:39.400 --> 37:39.900
Freeze?

37:40.440 --> 37:40.940
You...

37:41.110 --> 37:42.340
Enough. Let's go now!

37:43.230 --> 37:43.860
Get out!

37:46.550 --> 37:47.130
Di Zhu,

37:47.630 --> 37:48.650
I won't give up on you!

37:49.070 --> 37:50.380
You and the Star Stone are both mine!

37:51.670 --> 37:52.300
Man Man.

37:56.400 --> 37:57.170
Man Man,

37:57.760 --> 37:58.610
I roasted a leg of lamb for you.

37:59.320 --> 37:59.940
Try it.

38:01.590 --> 38:02.380
It's really good.

38:03.150 --> 38:03.740
No, thanks.

38:04.510 --> 38:05.380
I'm a vegetarian.

38:08.550 --> 38:10.610
Master Chi Wen, are you sulking

38:10.880 --> 38:11.820
because he beat you?

38:12.710 --> 38:13.570
What, a Dragon Deity

38:13.630 --> 38:14.940
who's lived millions of years

38:14.960 --> 38:16.090
could be so childish?

38:17.400 --> 38:18.300
I already got back

38:18.320 --> 38:19.340
at him for you.

38:19.960 --> 38:20.900
Still not happy?

38:23.190 --> 38:23.980
If you don't want

38:24.000 --> 38:25.940
to be pushed around,

38:26.150 --> 38:27.530
why not use your power?

38:30.400 --> 38:31.010
Because...

38:32.110 --> 38:33.340
I'm Man Man now.

38:34.630 --> 38:35.860
Man Man and Wu Zhiqi

38:35.920 --> 38:37.300
are both Green Ape demons.

38:37.400 --> 38:38.650
They can control the wind and sand.

38:40.000 --> 38:40.740
Can you?

38:52.840 --> 38:53.490
I can't.

38:54.440 --> 38:55.610
My power is sealed.

38:56.880 --> 38:57.460
Why?

38:58.230 --> 38:58.980
Maybe...

39:00.800 --> 39:02.130
Man Man doesn't want to reveal himself.

39:03.760 --> 39:04.760
So now

39:04.760 --> 39:06.300
you're a mere mortal

39:06.510 --> 39:07.980
with none of your old might,

39:09.000 --> 39:10.900
a totally helpless dragon

39:11.400 --> 39:12.860
at my mercy, huh?

39:14.550 --> 39:16.130
Di Zhu is a mortal too.

39:17.360 --> 39:18.420
How come you can still

39:18.880 --> 39:20.650
use Formless Moon magic?

39:22.360 --> 39:23.380
I don't know.

39:25.360 --> 39:26.400
Maybe the Formless Moon

39:26.400 --> 39:27.950
is stronger than your Shilin Sect.

39:40.000 --> 39:41.410
The nine spots on your head

39:41.430 --> 39:42.300
are pretty.

39:44.950 --> 39:46.060
Let me call you

39:47.240 --> 39:47.980
Little Nine.

39:48.710 --> 39:50.090
Aren't you scared of it at all?

39:56.440 --> 39:57.940
Without Wangyan here,

39:58.480 --> 39:59.690
I am a little scared.

40:00.760 --> 40:01.490
But,

40:02.400 --> 40:04.090
I feel like she's nearby.

40:04.840 --> 40:06.210
You know why that is?

40:06.840 --> 40:07.530
I do.

40:08.920 --> 40:09.740
Because this is

40:09.800 --> 40:11.650
the past illusion inside the Star Stone.

40:13.030 --> 40:13.900
Your sister

40:15.360 --> 40:16.740
is probably in another illusion.

41:12.020 --> 41:17.460
[One hundred years ago, Flood Dragon tribe]

41:34.020 --> 41:35.180
♪It's your light♪

41:35.380 --> 41:37.260
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

41:37.420 --> 41:40.540
♪That set the night alight♪

41:40.900 --> 41:47.420
♪And lead me through the fight♪

41:49.180 --> 41:51.060
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

41:51.500 --> 41:55.940
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

41:56.740 --> 41:58.420
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

41:58.580 --> 42:03.980
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

42:04.740 --> 42:10.140
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

42:12.460 --> 42:18.500
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

42:19.460 --> 42:21.620
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

42:21.900 --> 42:26.740
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

42:27.100 --> 42:29.420
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

42:29.620 --> 42:34.700
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

42:34.940 --> 42:36.940
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

42:37.220 --> 42:41.580
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

42:42.580 --> 42:49.540
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

43:06.100 --> 43:09.060
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

43:10.140 --> 43:13.540
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

43:14.340 --> 43:16.860
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

43:17.100 --> 43:20.180
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

43:20.580 --> 43:22.900
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

43:23.420 --> 43:27.820
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

43:28.060 --> 43:30.220
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

43:30.620 --> 43:35.580
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

43:35.820 --> 43:36.980
♪It's your light♪

43:37.180 --> 43:39.020
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

43:39.220 --> 43:42.340
♪That set the night alight♪

43:43.100 --> 43:52.540
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
